[21/10/2018 20:20:42] <font color="#ffffff">Karlos.</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:43] <font color="#ffffff">¡Si, señor!</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:45] <font color="#ffffff">¡Bien!</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:46] <font color="#ffffff">¡Si, señor!</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:50] <font color="#ffffff">¡Cayó clavado!</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:52] <font color="#ffffff">¡Qué bien!</font>
[21/10/2018 20:20:59] <font color="#ffffff">Vamos, Luca.</font>
[21/10/2018 20:21:01] <font color="#ffffff">¿OK?</font>
[21/10/2018 20:21:04] <font color="#ffffff">"AI subir al barco,</font>
